The paper deals with the optimization of computation and communication power in multi-user massive MIMO systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), architecture (cs.AR), and multimedia (cs.MM). The focus on massive MIMO and millimeter wave technology also suggests a possible connection to signal processing (cs.SP). However, since the paper does not explicitly mention signal processing, it is not included in the list.
